---
title: Easy Pulled Sesame Chicken Poke Bowl with Miso Roasted Kumara & Slaw
description: This blissful bowl rivals what you'd get at your local poke joint. Better yet, you can make it in a flash thanks to our slow-cooked
chicken breast, spiked with creamy sesame dressing; simply shred it and forget it while the kumara and rice cook.

